file.name: notice_openapi.yaml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    GoogleProtobufTimestamp:
      properties:
        nanos:
          description: Non-negative fractions of a second at nanosecond resolution.
            Negative second values with fractions must still have non-negative nanos
            values that count forward in time. Must be from 0 to 999,999,999 inclusive.
          format: int32
          type: integer
        seconds:
          description: Represents seconds of UTC time since Unix epoch 1970-01-01T00:00:00Z.
            Must be from 0001-01-01T00:00:00Z to 9999-12-31T23:59:59Z inclusive.
          format: int64
          type: integer
      type: object
    NewsV1Notice:
      properties:
        birthday:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/GoogleProtobufTimestamp'
        content:
          description: 通知内容
          type: string
        error_msg:
          description: 失败原因
          type: string
        status:
          description: 状态 0未发送 9发送成功 10 发送失败
          format: int32
          type: integer
        title:
          description: 标题
          type: string
        to:
          description: 接受者用户id
          type: string
        type:
          description: 通知类型 1 email 2 短信
          type: string
      type: object
    NewsV1NoticeCreateOption:
      properties:
        content:
          description: 通知内容
          type: string
        title:
          description: 标题
          type: string
        to:
          description: 接受者用户id
          type: string
        type:
          description: 通知类型 0 普通通知
          type: string
      type: object
    NewsV1NoticeList:
      properties:
        list:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/NewsV1Notice'
          type: array
        page:
          description: 页码
          format: int32
          type: integer
        page_size:
          description: 分页
          format: int32
          type: integer
        total:
          description: 总数
          format: int64
          type: integer
      type: object
info:
  description: news.v1
  title: news.v1
  version: "1"
openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
  /users/notice:
    description: 发送一个通知
    post:
      description: 发送一个通知
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/NewsV1NoticeCreateOption'
        description: 创建通知
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/NewsV1Notice'
          description: ok
      summary: 发送一个通知
      tags:
      - news.v1.NoticeService
    summary: Send
tags:
- description: 通知服务
  name: news.v1.NoticeService
